Confirm delete operation

Are you sure you want to delete this Property?

import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { NgbActiveModal } from '@ng-bootstrap/ng-bootstrap'; import { IProperty } from '../property.model'; import { PropertyService } from '../service/property.service'; @Component({ templateUrl: './property-delete-dialog.component.html', }) export class PropertyDeleteDialogComponent { property?: IProperty; constructor(protected propertyService: PropertyService, protected activeModal: NgbActiveModal) {} cancel(): void { this.activeModal.dismiss(); } confirmDelete(id: number): void { this.propertyService.delete(id).subscribe(() => { this.activeModal.close('deleted'); }); } }
